value: Breeds on the Aleutian Islands and on both sides of the North Pacific (chiefly on islands) from Kamchatka to Hokkaido and Korea, and from Sitka, Alaska to Washington. Winters chiefly at sea south to Japan and northern Lower California.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Mostly pelagic; nests on islands in ground burrows.

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip

value: ground displays only, including displays on trees and bushes
